<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>網頁設計 · 讓您的店被看見</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@300;400;600&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:      #F5F0EB;
  --bg2:     #EDEBE6;
  --bg3:     #E5E1DA;
  --white:   #FAF8F5;
  --text:    #2A2520;
  --text2:   #5A5550;
  --muted:   #9A9490;
  --line:    #D8D4CE;
  --accent:  #3D3830;
  --red:     #C0392B;
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── TOP BAR ── */
#topbar {
  position: fixed;
  top:0; left:0; right:0;
  z-index: 100;
  height: 52px;
  background: rgba(245,240,235,0.95);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 3rem;
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
}
.topbar-logo {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.topbar-nav {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
}
.topbar-nav a {
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--text2);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.topbar-nav a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

/* ── HERO ── */
#hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding-top: 52px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-left {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 6rem 4rem 6rem 3rem;
  background: var(--white);
}
.hero-right {
  background: var(--bg3);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.hero-right-pattern {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  opacity: 0.35;
  background-image:
    repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 40px, var(--line) 40px, var(--line) 41px),
    repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 40px, var(--line) 40px, var(--line) 41px);
}
.hero-right-center {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}
.hero-circle {
  width: 220px;
  height: 220px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  background: var(--white);
}
.hero-circle-inner {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 38px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--accent);
  line-height: 1;
}
.hero-circle-sub {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-top: 6px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.hero-eyebrow {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.4;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.hero-title strong {
  font-weight: 600;
  display: block;
}
.hero-body {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 2;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  max-width: 400px;
}
.hero-cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg);
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 13px 28px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.25s;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
}
.hero-cta:hover { background: var(--text); }
.hero-cta-ghost {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  background: none;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 13px 28px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.25s;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  margin-left: 1rem;
}
.hero-cta-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2.5rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
  padding-top: 2rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.hero-stat-num {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  color: var(--accent);
  line-height: 1;
}
.hero-stat-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

/* ── SECTIONS ── */
.section {
  padding: 7rem 3rem;
  max-width: 1080px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.section-sm {
  padding: 5rem 3rem;
  max-width: 1080px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.sec-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.4em;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.sec-label::before {
  content: '';
  width: 24px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--muted);
}
.sec-heading {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
  font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 38px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--accent);
  line-height: 1.4;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.sec-heading strong { font-weight: 600; }
.sec-body {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 2;
  max-width: 520px;
}

/* ── DIVIDER ── */
.divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--line);
  margin: 0 3rem;
}

/* ── WHAT I DO ── */
#services { background: var(--white); }
.services-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
  gap: 5rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.service-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
.service-item {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 1.75rem 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}
.service-item:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
.service-num {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.service-name {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.service-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
}
.service-item:hover .service-desc { max-height: 80px; color: var(--text2); }

.service-right {
  padding-top: 1rem;
}
.service-visual {
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 3rem;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  background-color: var(--line);
}
.sv-item {
  background: var(--bg);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.sv-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.sv-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text2); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

/* ── PLANS ── */
.plans-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1px;
  background: var(--line);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  margin-top: 3rem;
}
.plan {
  background: var(--white);
  padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
.plan:hover { background: var(--bg2); }
.plan.featured {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg);
}
.plan.featured:hover { background: var(--text); }
.plan-tag {
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.plan.featured .plan-tag { color: rgba(245,240,235,0.5); }
.plan-name-text {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.plan.featured .plan-name-text { color: var(--bg); }
.plan-amount {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 48px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--accent);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.plan.featured .plan-amount { color: var(--bg); }
.plan-currency {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.plan.featured .plan-currency { color: rgba(245,240,235,0.5); }
.plan-sep {
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--line);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.plan.featured .plan-sep { background: rgba(245,240,235,0.15); }
.plan-items {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.625rem;
  flex: 1;
}
.plan-items li {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 8px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.plan.featured .plan-items li { color: rgba(245,240,235,0.8); }
.plan-items li.off { color: var(--muted); opacity: 0.5; }
.plan-items li::before {
  content: '—';
  color: var(--muted);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-size: 11px;
}
.plan.featured .plan-items li::before { color: rgba(245,240,235,0.4); }
.plan-btn-wrap { margin-top: 2rem; }
.plan-btn {
  display: block;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 11px 0;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  cursor: pointer;
  border: none;
  width: 100%;
}
.plan-btn.dark {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg);
}
.plan-btn.dark:hover { background: var(--text); }
.plan-btn.light {
  background: none;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  color: var(--text2);
}
.plan-btn.light:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
.plan-btn.inv {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--accent);
}
.plan-btn.inv:hover { background: var(--bg3); }

/* ── ADDONS ── */
.addon-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin-top: 2rem;
}
.addon-table tr {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  transition: background 0.15s;
}
.addon-table tr:hover { background: var(--bg2); }
.addon-table td {
  padding: 1rem 0.5rem;
  font-size: 13px;
}
.addon-table td:first-child { color: var(--text2); }
.addon-table td:last-child {
  text-align: right;
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--accent);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.addon-table th {
  padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.addon-table th:last-child { text-align: right; }

/* ── GUARANTEE ── */
.guarantee-box {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: center;
}
.g-num {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 72px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--line);
  line-height: 1;
}
.g-title {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.g-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.9; }

/* ── HOW ── */
#how { background: var(--bg2); }
.how-steps {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 0;
  margin-top: 3rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.how-step {
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
  position: relative;
  background: var(--white);
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.how-step:last-child { border-right: none; }
.how-step:hover { background: var(--bg); }
.how-n {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 36px;
  color: var(--line);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.how-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.how-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

/* ── PAIN ── */
.pain-cols {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.pain-list { list-style: none; margin-top: 1rem; }
.pain-list li {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 1.25rem 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 1rem;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text2);
  line-height: 1.7;
}
.pain-list li .pi { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.pain-right-block {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg);
  padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
  position: sticky;
  top: 6rem;
}
.pain-right-block .sec-heading { color: var(--bg); font-size: 22px; }
.pain-right-block .sec-body { color: rgba(245,240,235,0.7); max-width: none; }
.prb-stat {
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
.prb-row { border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,240,235,0.15); padding-top: 1.25rem; }
.prb-num {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 40px;
  color: var(--bg);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.prb-label { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(245,240,235,0.5); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

/* ── CTA SECTION ── */
#contact {
  background: var(--white);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.contact-inner {
  padding: 7rem 3rem;
  max-width: 1080px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 5rem;
  align-items: center;
}
.contact-left .sec-heading { font-size: clamp(26px,3vw,42px); }
.contact-form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.25rem;
}
.cf-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
  display: block;
}
.cf-input {
  width: 100%;
  background: var(--bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  color: var(--text);
  font-size: 13px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.cf-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
.cf-select {
  width: 100%;
  background: var(--bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  color: var(--text);
  font-size: 13px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.cf-select option { background: var(--bg); }
.cf-submit {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg);
  border: none;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 14px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  transition: background 0.2s;
  width: 100%;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}
.cf-submit:hover { background: var(--text); }
.cf-note {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  padding: 3rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  background: var(--bg);
}
.footer-brand {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.footer-copy {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

/* ── REVEAL ── */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
}
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* ── SUCCESS ── */
#form-success {
  display: none;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 3rem;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
}
#form-success .fs-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
#form-success .fs-title {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
#form-success .fs-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  #hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero-right { display: none; }
  .services-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .plans-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .how-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .pain-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; text-align: center; }
  #topbar { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .topbar-nav { display: none; }
  .section, .section-sm { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── TOP BAR ── -->
<div id="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-logo">Web Design Studio</div>
  <nav class="topbar-nav">
    <a href="#services">服務項目</a>
    <a href="#pricing">方案報價</a>
    <a href="#how">合作流程</a>
    <a href="#contact">立即諮詢</a>
  </nav>
</div>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">餐廳網頁設計 · 數位品牌建立</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      讓您的餐廳<br>
      <strong>被全世界看見</strong>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-body">專為台灣餐廳打造的多語系官網，內建線上訂位與後台管理。從設計到上線，讓客人 24 小時都能找到您。</p>
    <div>
      <a href="#pricing" class="hero-cta">查看方案 →</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="hero-cta-ghost">免費諮詢</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-stat-num">4</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">語言支援</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-stat-num">7天</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">最快交付</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-stat-num">NT$0</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">先看草稿再付款</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="hero-right-pattern"></div>
    <div class="hero-right-center">
      <div class="hero-circle">
        <div class="hero-circle-inner">網</div>
        <div class="hero-circle-sub">Web Design</div>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.15em;">設計 · 開發 · 上線</p>
      <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;letter-spacing:0.08em;">DESIGN · BUILD · LAUNCH</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── PROBLEM ── -->
<section class="section reveal">
  <div class="pain-cols">
    <div>
      <p class="sec-label">您目前面臨的問題</p>
